## 🛠️ Project Structure

```text
pr_rev/
├── main.py                # FastAPI Application & Endpoints
├── agents.py              # LangGraph Agents & Dough.id Integration
├── github_utils.py        # GitHub REST API interactions
├── requirements.txt       # Python dependencies
├── .env                   # Environment variables
└── frontend/
